        "text": "οὕτω",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", in these circumstances; that is, thus upheld by a promise and an oath. The oath warned him of trial. It would not have been given had the promise been a trifling one or had it been destined for immediate fulfilment. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "f1μακροθυμήσας",
        "children": []
