        "class": "ital",
        "text": "long",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " kept up his courage and his hope. Delay followed delay; disappointment followed disappointment. He was driven out of the promised land, and a barren wife mocked the hope of the promised seed, but he waited expectant, and at length ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ἐπέτυχε τῆς ἐπαγγελίας",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", for although it was true of him, as of all O.T. saints, that he did ",
        "children": []
